content: I think I'm looking for someone who's genuine, kind, and can make me laugh. Both Ryan and Alex seem to have those qualities, but in different ways. Ryan's more outgoing and funny, while Alex is more laid-back and easy-going. I'm not sure which direction I'm leaning yet, but I'm excited to get to know them both better. Do you have any advice on how to navigate this situation without leading either of them on or getting hurt myself?
